{"tid":1611761,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家講嘢小心啲！","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:40:05.000Z","uid":272200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c50289618ad018898161587bafaf39b6b9762251","tid":1611761,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:50:14.000Z","msg":"我唔知你地講緊咩（我剩係發夢架咋），但我見人又話火又話刀，各位緊張之餘，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好唔記得左你地用咩電腦，邊間ISP，咩IP，咩電郵登記上連登呀</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n事後追究起來，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登俾法院出 subpoena，都係要交資料架！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3950830f97cdf899bcac5df5e02cd3470377a898","tid":1611761,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"9ca6285054ef4facdf52f6b0e46f7682f883b794","tid":1611761,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"外國server香港法庭管唔管到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef465029b565c1715ca4c63716aa1433a7c6303","tid":1611761,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"必要時買二手電腦用公共Wi-Fi"},{"pid":"dbd7e28fe99c34e02b7a7c221a8513882792e37b","tid":1611761,"uid":19992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ef465029b565c1715ca4c63716aa1433a7c6303","tid":1611761,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"必要時買二手電腦用公共Wi-Fi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"Isp email呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad311a2d49487c4258b24684b6f6b639bb72989","tid":1611761,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca6285054ef4facdf52f6b0e46f7682f883b794","tid":1611761,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"外國server香港法庭管唔管到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"如果連登老細好似 Telegram 既 Pavel Durov 咁全隊人全球走都還好，但如果唔係，照告你出Warrant 通緝你，攪你公司你屋企人迫你跪低，你咪一樣要交！<br />\n<br />\n政府法律攻擊有心人對冇心人，你好難避得哂，如果系統係同大陸 friend既地方有 staging copy既話 （我講緊例如，唔係依家係咁），就大Q鑊<br />\n<br />\n大家小心d唔好咁易俾人入，加重連登風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48990779ea949d07d78fd4eb62dad35e6c71c84","tid":1611761,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"3b17ff94e8a2df7312b05a659cb8b15858bf2013","tid":1611761,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n連登資料連連仔都拎唔到出嚟<br />\n單向加密放咗喺美國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122db60234899bc5e19a4c7a1ee55fe942c3a0c9","tid":1611761,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f4cec62ce051cdd09c8dbff54c5bdbcc92e37e2","tid":1611761,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b17ff94e8a2df7312b05a659cb8b15858bf2013","tid":1611761,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n連登資料連連仔都拎唔到出嚟<br />\n單向加密放咗喺美國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"好啦咁你有名有姓講犯法野啦，on9<br />\n<br />\n連仔自己都拎唔到出來係基本好無？佢拎唔到出來，就代表系統無bug，唔會有人拎到出來？<br />\n<br />\n重有，所有網上事物都差不多是永恆保存。今日攞唔到唔代表將來攞唔到。認為世界上有一個永不能破既電腦系統和法律安排，證明你係一個嫌命長既死蠢<br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔信連登。佢呢一百日都無咩點死，已經好厲害，我無野要教佢地。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我講既係你地唔好大安旨意，自己都要小心呀！</span></span>"}]}